                "history": [
                    {
                        "changed": "2025-12-23T00:00:00-06:00",
                        "changes": "An updated version of this title is now available.Leviatham's Size changed, dragons are immune to fire."
                    },
                    {
                        "changed": "2025-11-30T00:00:00-06:00",
                        "changes": "An updated version of this title is now available. This PDF corrects the instruction ro reduce the Type 3 demon's Health. Apologies. "
                    },
                    {
                        "changed": "2025-11-24T00:00:00-06:00",
                        "changes": "After some feedback, I went through all the enemies and recalculated their Difficulty scores. This looks a bit more than it actually is. Really, most Difficulties climbed by one to two spots, while I shrank a few Diff 1 enemies to make them behave more as fodder. A few revisions appear in this document, but they are minor. Also, this PDF includes updtaed encounter building guidelines. Thanks for your patience and your support!"
                    },
                    {
                        "changed": "2024-08-18T00:00:00-05:00",
                        "changes": "Hey gang! I'm including a hi-res version of the map so that you can print it out, zoom in, and do all that fun stuff. It's a big file, but here we are. Thanks for your support and happy gaming!"
                    },
                    {
                        "changed": "2024-07-05T00:00:00-05:00",
                        "changes": "An updated version of this title is now available. We squashed a few typos and corrected some layout glitches. Index and ToC repaired. Thanks for your patience!"
                    },
                    {
                        "changed": "2024-06-20T00:00:00-05:00",
                        "changes": "We've uploaded a low res version for you. Enjoy!"
                    },
                    {
                        "changed": "2024-06-19T00:00:00-05:00",
                        "changes": "Here it is! The complete version of Secrets of the Weird Wizard is yours! Thanks for your patience and your keen eyes!"
                    },
                    {
                        "changed": "2024-06-19T00:00:00-05:00",
                        "changes": "This version repairs the typo on the back cover, corrects the credits, and shrinks the file size a bit. We'll do a bigger compression soon for low-res folks."
                    },
                    {
                        "changed": "2024-06-05T00:00:00-05:00",
                        "changes": "An updated version of this title is now available. This is still not the final, but it's much, much closer. We have some placeholders here and there and some tweaking to make, plus the cover, but this is almost done. Thanks for your patience!"
                    },
                    {
                        "changed": "2024-05-15T00:00:00-05:00",
                        "changes": "This file collects the front matter and chapters 1 and 2. It's almost final. Chapter 3 should be along in another two weeks. If you see anything weird, please post on the Schwalb Entertainment discord channel. Thanks!"
                    },
                    {
                        "changed": "2024-04-09T00:00:00-05:00",
                        "changes": "Minor revisions to text. Ancestry review complete and synched with Weird Ancestries supplement. ."
                    },
